data.description: Highly desirable Windsor Ridge! You will be awed upon approach by the meticulously landscaped lot, including a front patio area with firepit. The detailed paint work on the home sets it apart from all others. Inside, you will be greeted by vaulted ceilings, a large and sunny living room, separate formal dining area leading into a large family room with a cozy fireplace. Brand new HVAC and windows! The charming kitchen with extra dining area makes you feel right at home. Nothing to do but move in! The sprawlig backyard is fully privacy fenced and includes a wooden deck, beautiful trees and berry bushes, and a pea gravel fire pit area. Upstairs you will find 4 spacious bedrooms including the Primary Suite with the most spectacular en suite bathroom that is one of the biggest selling points of this home. You will never want to leave this spa-like retreat! An additional full bathroom is available upstairs and a powder room downstairs gives this home the perfect layout. Upstairs mudroom is hooked up for laundry, current owners just prefers it in the basement. The unfinished basement is ready for your touches and is already plumbed for a bathroom, and a separate bedroom is framed for all the additional space you will need. Welcome home!
